## Executing e2e tests

### Prepare local test environment with python:
```bash
python3 -m venv .venv
pip install -r tests/requirements.txt
```

### Generate SSL files
To prepare SSL files required for testings execute:
```bash
cd tests/
./gencerts_shell.sh
chmod ugoa+rw certs/*.pem
```

## Access modes of docker generated files
You may need to tweak access modes of files in tests/certs/ and in tests/logs/
```bash
touch logs/mysqld0.log
touch logs/mysqld1.log
touch logs/mysqld2.log
chmod ugoa+rw logs/*.log
```

### Execute e2e tests:
```bash
cd tests/
./gencerts_shell.sh
pytest
```

